title: Fair Trade Cafe - Civic Space Park
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Downstairs fair trade coffee house and juice bar with vegan lunch food like a hummus sandwich, salads, and occasional weekly special; plus a few vegan baked goods like brownies and cookies. Some items can be made vegan by excluding cheese. Brunch on Sunday. Free Wi-Fi.
